title: AFC Free Agency Grades: The Patriots Post-Tom Brady Plan, Texans flunk offseason (Football 3/24)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jason La Canfora to grade the free agency moves of all AFC Teams...Patriots (4:50), Dolphins (19:05), Bills (23:40), Jets (28:30), Browns (34:50), Ravens (36:30), Bengals (41:00), Steelers (45:20), Texans (47:30), Colts (49:00), Titans (52:10), Jaguars (54:30), Raiders (57:00), Chargers (59:15), Broncos (1:01:45) and Chiefs (1:02:30)
